PASSIONATE IS OUT EVERYWHERE MIDNIGHT !⁣

Wrote this in the lab w my brother @kidculture who also produced THE FUCK outta this track.⁣
⁣

So excited for you to listen i know you’re gonna love it 🩶

I’m so fucking happy to be back and releasing new music again. PASSIONATE IS FINALLY OUT and i just wanna thank you all for sticking w me through the years. You guys have been asking why i went away for so long and that’s because i needed to go away to get to know myself.

It’s been a long fluctuating journey and I’m still only halfway through it but I’ve learned and have grown a ton which led me to find my passion for all aspects of life once again. 

As well through that time i locked in with a solid collaborative crew whom have become family to me. And lemme tell you we made some of the BEST music and It’ll all be on one album. My new album, As Far As The Eye Can See, dropping in 2024. 
⁣
can’t wait for you to experience AFATECS 👁️
